'''Gueye Seydinaissa Laye''' ({{Langx|ar|عيسى لاي}}; born 22 December 1997) is a professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|center back]] for [[Qatar Stars League]] club [[Al-Arabi SC (Qatar)|Al-Arabi]].  Born in [[Senegal]], he represents the [[Qatar national football team|Qatar national team]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Issa Laye|url=https://www.365scores.com/football/player/issa-laye-181780|website=365scores.com}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://alarabi.qa/player/%d9%8a%d9%88%d8%b3%d9%81-%d8%a7%d9%84%d9%85%d8%b3%d8%a7%d9%83%d9%86%d9%8a/|title=Issa Laye|website=alarabi.qa}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.worldfootball.net/person/pe1460588/issa-laye/#google_vignette|title=Issa Laye|website=worldfootball.net}}</ref>

==Club career==
On 1 July 2020, Laye joined side [[Lusail SC|Lusail]] in [[Qatari Second Division]]. On 10 September 2024, Laye joined side [[Al-Shamal SC|Al-Shamal]] in [[Qatar Stars League]] on a one-year loan<ref>{{cite web |title=الدوري القطري.. نادي الشمال يتعاقد مع المدافع السنغالي عيسى لاي على سبيل الإعارة|url=https://qna.org.qa/ar-QA/news/news-details?id=0138-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AF%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%82%D8%B7%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B4%D9%85%D8%A7%D9%84-%D9%8A%D8%AA%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%82%D8%AF-%D9%85%D8%B9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%81%D8%B9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B3%D9%86%D8%BA%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8A-%D8%B9%D9%8A%D8%B3%D9%89-%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%8A-%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%89-%D8%B3%D8%A8%D9%8A%D9%84-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A5%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%A9&date=10/09/2024}}</ref> On 30 January 2025, Laye joined side [[Al-Arabi SC (Qatar)|Al-Arabi]] in [[Qatar Stars League]] on a half-year loan.<ref>{{cite web |title=عيسى لاي عرباوي|url=https://alarabi.qa/%D8%B9%D9%8A%D8%B3%D9%89-%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%8A-%D8%B9%D8%B1%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%88%D9%8A/}}</ref> On 18 July 2025, Laye moved to [[Al-Arabi SC (Qatar)|Al-Arabi]] permanently and signed a five-year contract.<ref>{{cite web |title=تجديد التعاقد مع عيسى لاي حتى 2030|url=https://alarabi.qa/%D8%AA%D8%AC%D8%AF%D9%8A%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%82%D8%AF-%D9%85%D8%B9-%D8%B9%D9%8A%D8%B3%D9%89-%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%8A-%D8%AD%D8%AA%D9%89-2030/}}</ref>

==International career==
In 2025, Laye obtained [[Qatari nationality law|Qatari citizenship]] and was selected to join the [[Qatar national football team|Qatar national team]] to participate at the [[2025 FIFA Arab Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://qna.org.qa/ar-QA/news/news-details?id=%D9%83%D8%A7%D8%B3-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%B1%D8%A8-fifa-%D9%82%D8%B7%D8%B1-2025-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B9%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%B9%D9%86-%D9%82%D8%A7%D9%8A%D9%85%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%AE%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%82%D8%B7%D8%B1%D9%8A&date=23/11/2025|title=كأس العرب FIFA قطر 2025.. الإعلان عن قائمة المنتخب القطري}}</ref>

